other model, also solvable by our\nmethods, which never reaches a steady state, the uncertainty function, is in\nsome cases, bounded from below by a value less than $2k_BT$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 16:52:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Mar 2018 10:49:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-13"}
