rea is determined by land use intensity. These findings support the\nnotion that multifunctional rural landscapes provide multiple ES, making an\nimportant contribution to human well-being, and that land use planning that\ndevelops green infrastructure in urban areas can significantly contribute to\nsupport biodiversity and ES delivery.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Dec 2017 20:10:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-21"}
